com.magicbinder.criterias.base

Class Criterion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.magicbinder.criterias.base.Criterion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICriteria, java.io.Serializable

    public class Criterion
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, ICriteria
    Criteria. Criteria used for some db requests. A criteria reprensents a condition (ie. "id = 2"). It is composed of: - a key (ie. "id") - a Type (ie. "EQUALS") - a value (ie. 2)
